                  </hi>. About eight o'clock that evening the two prisoners came to me—they offered these things for sale, and asked me 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. for them—I gave it them—I asked them who sent them, and they said their</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184508180133"></xptr>
               <p>mother—I asked where they lived, and they said at No. 21, Clement's-lane, but it was a false address.</p>
